\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506   2. The system fetches and displays a list of all existing facilities that is specified with filters.
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506   3. The user selects a specific date and time if the specified facility or facilities are available.
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506   4. The system queries the database to calculate free slots and updates the UI.
