\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\ai\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\i\cf21\insrsid5197426\charrsid5197426 \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506     - Frontend (UI): Displays the facility list and provides date/time selection components.
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506     - Backend (Logic): Calculates availability logic by querying existing reservations against the requested time slots.
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506     - Database: Executes queries to fetch facility data and reservation statuses.
\par 
