\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506   2. The user attempts to confirm the reservation.
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506   3. The system checks the user's role to ensure they have not exceeded the maximum active reservation limit (X).
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506   4. If the limit is not exceeded, the system performs validation and concurrency checks to prevent double booking.
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506   5. The system successfully stores the reservation details (user, facility, date, start time, end time) in the database.
