\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\ai\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\i\cf21\insrsid5197426\charrsid5197426 \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506     - Frontend (UI): Allows users to select time slots and displays success or warning messages.
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506     - Backend (Logic): Enforces limit checks (count queries) and utilizes database locking/concurrency checks for safe booking.
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506     - Database: Stores the new reservation records.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\ai\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\i\cf20\insrsid5197426\charrsid862242 \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 Use case 4: Priority Conflict Handling
