\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506     - Database: Updates the status of the affected reservations to reflect cancellations and new bookings.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\ai\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\i\cf21\insrsid5197426\charrsid5197426 
